Text: Sorry about the double-upload.  Had a problem with the trackers on the first one.

I have set up a poster here (and on demonoid), who is very reliable - with my Rush podcasts and morning updates. 

I enjoy Rush too much not to contribute in some way.
i have deleted the other one for you :)

Podcast is up.  For obvious reasons, if someone (like sharky) posts a radio rip, it will almost always beat the podcast.  I have no problem continuing to provide the podcasts while a radio rip goes up.

RESIST WE MUCH!

Thank you very much to both of you Sharky and Nico!!!
